<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<dashboard>
  <label>Welcome</label>
  <row>
    <html>
      <h2>Welcome to the X-ray Splunk app!</h2>

      <p>This app is designed to help you understand the dependencies between knowledge objects. It can answer questions such as
      </p>
      <list>
        <li>Where is the tag "dmz" used in my Splunk environment? <a href="where_is_it_used">[Hint]</a></li>
        <li>Where is the search "Top users by day" defined? <a href="ko_search_by_name_and_tupe">[Hint]</a></li>
      </list>

      <p>This app does not address all knowledge objects. It records the following for the various types:
      </p>
      <table border="1" cellpadding="2">
        <tr>
          <th>Type</th>
          <th>Identifies where the <br/> object is <strong>defined</strong></th>
          <th>Identifies where the <br/>object is <strong>used</strong></th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Saved Searches</td><td align="center">yes</td><td align="center">yes</td>
        </tr>
        <tr><td>Eventtypes</td><td align="center">yes</td><td align="center">yes</td>
        </tr>
        <tr><td>Tags</td><td align="center">yes</td><td align="center">yes</td>
        </tr>
        <tr><td>Fields</td><td align="center">-</td><td align="center">-</td>
        </tr>
        <tr><td>Lookups</td><td align="center">yes</td><td align="center">yes</td>
        </tr>
				<tr><td>Macros</td><td align="center">yes</td><td align="center">yes</td>
        </tr>
        <tr><td>Dashboards - simple XML</td><td align="center">yes</td><td align="center">-</td>
        </tr>
				<tr><td>Forms - simple XML</td><td align="center">yes</td><td align="center">-</td>
        </tr>
				<tr><td>Views - advanced XML</td><td align="center">yes</td><td align="center">-</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br/><p>Note that it does not analyze automatic lookups or their effects.</p>
    </html>
  </row>
</dashboard>
